{"tid":1485672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公民抗命，不分和勇！","createTime":"2019-08-18T16:25:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T16:43:02.000Z","uid":309398,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e763b8c36fa15d75b8d0bd35c0cc839a0a43264e","tid":1485672,"uid":309398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:25:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「公民抗命，不分和勇！」</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">「公民抗命，不分和勇！」</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「公民抗命，不分和勇！」</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下次和理非回合就講哩句口號<br />\n1.對前線嘅鼓勵性更甚「香港人加油」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.以口號方式表達不割席精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.去標籤化，溫和嘅手足會更接納前線行動升級，而前線手足會願意為溫和手足克制（就好似今日）<br />\n4.今日舉牌嗰位手足都係想我地更團結先講哩句！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170ed9a93c77f877e6fcfeec1e7ea0456d8cba4a","tid":1485672,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:26:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">【雨傘2.0】劉業成有心公開銅鑼灣班卧底 就係想大家一齊捉鬼</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1481711\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1481711</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0e1be20af15661d653c67aeec52c44cb8f8eb099","tid":1485672,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,